msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Jekk inti minn barra tal-U.S., nirrakkomandaw NOWPayments (komissi l-iktar "
"iżjed, direzzjoni tieħel il-wallet tiegħek). Jekk inti fil-U.S., Stripe "
"Crypto ukoll huwa għażla. Tista' tipponta servizzi multipli u tħalli "
"l-visitaturi jagħżlu!"

