"partijiet – biss il‑wallet tiegħek u servizzi free."

msgid ""
"Some browsers block third-party scripts for privacy. This proxy loads "
"scripts through your own server to bypass these blocks."
msgstr ""
"Baġeniet qabel maħżuma jibħex scripts ta’ terz partijiet għall‑privat. Dan "
"il‑proxy jibgħat scripts permezz tal‑server tiegħek biex jħallu "
"l‑blokkijiet."

